 {
  coords 2290.134 212.913 4044.012
  m_sTitle "Sustainment"
  m_sTextData "- MG Ammo is crossloaded."\
  "- 3x TOW Missiles in Tow Team Landie"\
  "- 2 Landies for Transport"\
  "- 1 Landie for Tow Team"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 {
  coords 2273.471 211.071 4045.192
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "a. Enemy Forces:"\
  "Enemy forces consist of a Soviet mechanized rifle battalion positioned to our south. It is assessed that they will deploy at least a company-sized element to intercept withdrawing friendly forces utilizing ASR CARBON. Enemy infantry are equipped with AK-pattern rifles, PK machine guns, and RPG anti-armor weapons. Mechanized support is expected to consist of BMP-2 infantry fighting vehicles."\
  ""\
  "b. Friendly Forces:"\
  "Third squad have suffered casualities from earlier recon probing attacks and are comabt inefective. We are located at Ruckberg and have an attached TOW Team (71A)."\
  ""\
  "Friendly convoy expects us to hold the ENY back for 45 mins."\
  ""\
  "c. Terrain"\
  "Terrain is open fields with small patches of dense foliage with a dominating ridge line to the south. We have very good sightlines of the whole AO from the ridgeline of Ruckberg."\
  ""\
  "d. Weather"\
  "Overcast."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 0
 }
 {
  coords 2319.698 214.905 4034.615
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "Delay the ENY from advancing and destroying retreating friendly forces on ASR Carbon."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 {
  coords 2303.692 213.706 4041.045
  m_sTitle "Command and Signal"
  m_sTextData "a. Command"\
  "Chain of command is: Plt Sjt > 1st Section > 2nd Section"\
  ""\
  "b. Signal"\
  "Platoon Net - 46MHz"\
  "Platoon HQ - 22"\
  "1st Section - 22 Alpha"\
  "2nd Section - 22 Bravo"\
  "TOW Team - 71 Alpha"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 {
  coords 2313.031 218.235 4027.35
  m_sTitle "Tow Team"
  m_sTextData "TOW Team you require the following items to assemble the TOW, they need to be placed on the ground close to the where the Tripod will be placed."\
  ""\
  "1.      Tripod (Backpack Slot)"\
  "2.      Launch Tube   (Backpack Slot)"\
  "3.      LBB (Backpack Slot)"\
  "4.      Aiming System (Goes into your backpack)"\
  "5.      FCS  (Goes into your backpack)"\
  "6.      TOW-2A RF  (Backpack Slot)"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
}